  "title": "Semigroup",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "A \\textbf{semigroup} is a pair $(A,\\star)$ where $A$ is a nonempty set and\n$\\star:A\\times A\\to A$ is an associative binary operation:\n\\[\n\\forall a,b,c \\in A,\\quad\n(a\\star b)\\star c=a\\star(b\\star c).\n\\]",
